Title: The Adventures of Ociee Nash
Writer: Amy McGary (screenplay), Kristen McGary (screenplay), Milam McGraw Propst (novel)
Actors: Skyler Day, Woofer, Anthony P. Rodriguez, Bill Butler
Plot: The Adventures of Ociee Nash tells the story of nine year old Ociee Nash in the year 1898 who is sent from her father and brothers in rural Mississippi to live with her refined aunt in Asheville, North Carolina.
